nodes.text:
A jungle was a type of ecosystem common across settled space. It was characteri
zed by dense vegetation, high rainfall, and tropical climates. Many jungles were home to a large variety of plant and animal life. Typically, forests thrived at lower temperatures than jungles.
Planets with jungle environments included Akiva,Anaxes, D'Qar, Devaron, Felucia, Konkiv, Numidian Prime, Trandosha, and Zeitooine,
